### ============================================================
###  S03-26 Web App — Contactos API
###  Base URL: http://localhost:3001
###  Usar con la extensión REST Client (VS Code)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@contactId = 2889ddcb-61f6-4bee-a100-f9c2e2d9d0ef

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 👥 CONTACTOS — Endpoints para gestión de contactos
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [1] Obtener todos los contactos
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Crear un nuevo contacto
# @name createContact
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "email": "juan.perez@example.com",
  "phone": "+123456789",
  "segmentType": "lead"
}

###

### [3] Obtener un contacto por ID
# Reemplaza el ID con uno real obtenido del GET ALL

GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Actualizar un contacto (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lastName": "Pérez Modificado",
  "segmentType": "client"
}

###

### [5] Eliminar un contacto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contacts/{{contactId}}
Accept: application/json

###
